## 4. Known Issues\par
\par
> [!WARNING]\par
> **Identical Patterns in Specific Implementations**\par
> Under certain conditions, specifically when using the Rust native implementations of **`Philox32`** and **`Pcg32`**, they may generate identical random number sequences or identical patterns depending on the initial seed and internal state configuration. Please be cautious when using these specific implementations if strict uniqueness across different seeds is required.\par
\par
